title: Wati - Na Only Me Dey
seo_description: A song wrapped around God's amazing love and how he pours it out on every one of us. The song, produced by prolific producer Johnny Drille is inspirational and gives hope to as many who may still be wandering, that there's someone who loves them and is waiting and watching for them to come home.
description:
<!--StartFragment-->

A song wrapped around God's amazing love and how he pours it out on every one of us. The song, produced by prolific producer Johnny Drille is inspirational and gives hope to as many who may still be wandering, that there's someone who loves them and is waiting and watching for them to come home.
